  "detailed_description": "<h1>Steam Greenlight</h1><p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>INVISIBLE GHOST</u></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751470/extras/5e4c5e6d2ff934b8377cfe62c74bf6e4.poster.avif?t=1732609339\" width=608 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751470/extras/5e4c5e6d2ff934b8377cfe62c74bf6e4.webm?t=1732609339\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/751470/extras/5e4c5e6d2ff934b8377cfe62c74bf6e4.mp4?t=1732609339\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u>GAME DESCRIPTION</u></h2>The Deadstep is a first-person psychological horror game that achieves simple goals.<br><br><br>One day, you have a nightmare of being chased by a ghost for five days.<br><br>You are stuck in a mysterious place and though you look around for help, but it seems to be no one there.<br><br>Despite the footsteps that you’ve heard from somewhere, you can't still see anything around.<br><br>The sounds get closer and closer. At that moment, you can see a bloody footprint being stamped on the floor.<br><br>It was an invisible ghost who lives there and tries to hurt you by screaming to get you out of there.<br><br>To survive, after finding items that are necessary for the exorcism you have to do a ritual to defeat the ghost. Be careful about the ghost's footprints and footsteps.<br><br><br>Find the items and survive before the ghost finds you!",
